    "With just five uncalibrated handheld human videos-featuring different backgrounds and object positions-TraceGen attains 67.5% realrobot success.",
    "IntroductionRobots are expected to master diverse manipulation tasks across platforms and scenes, yet collecting sufficient, taskspecific robot demonstrations is slow and costly.",
